params.name: num_channels
params.description: The number of input channels.

params.name: image_size
params.description: The input image size.

params.name: width_coefficient
params.description: Scaling coefficient for network width at each stage.

params.name: depth_coefficient
params.description: Scaling coefficient for network depth at each stage.

params.name: depth_divisor
params.description: A unit of network width.

params.name: kernel_sizes
params.description: List of kernel sizes to be used in each block.

params.name: in_channels
params.description: List of input channel sizes to be used in each block for convolutional layers.

params.name: out_channels
params.description: List of output channel sizes to be used in each block for convolutional layers.

params.name: depthwise_padding
params.description: List of block indices with square padding.

params.name: strides
params.description: List of stride sizes to be used in each block for convolutional layers.

params.name: num_block_repeats
params.description: List of the number of times each block is to repeated.

params.name: expand_ratios
params.description: List of scaling coefficient of each block.

params.name: squeeze_expansion_ratio
params.description: Squeeze expansion ratio.

params.name: hidden_act
params.description: The non-linear activation function (function or string) in each block. If string, gelu, relu,selu, gelu_new, siluandmish` are supported.

params.name: hidden_dim
params.description: The hidden dimension of the layer before the classification head.

params.name: pooling_type
params.description: Type of final pooling to be applied before the dense classification head. Available options are [mean,max]

params.name: initializer_range
params.description: The standard deviation of the truncated_normal_initializer for initializing all weight matrices.

params.name: batch_norm_eps
params.description: The epsilon used by the batch normalization layers.

params.name: batch_norm_momentum
params.description: The momentum used by the batch normalization layers.

params.name: drop_connect_rate
params.description: The drop rate for skip connections.
